  "lessonText": "Explore the foundational ideas of 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' and their importance in early childhood development.",
  "data": {
    "content": "• 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' represents essential sounds in early childhood communication.\n• These playful sounds aid in language development and cognitive skills.\n• Understanding these sounds helps caregivers support children's growth.\n• Engaging with 'Gu Gu Ga Ga' fosters creativity and social interaction.\n• Practicing these sounds can enhance listening and speaking abilities."
